title: Californian high school turns down $10,000 prize and a visit from Macklemore
text: Californian high school turns down $10,000 prize and a visit from Macklemore Tuesday, 13 October 2015 (12 minutes ago) Aliso Niguel High School received complaints from parents for 'misogyny' and 'drug use' in the hip hop duo's music
